title: Two Americans, including one member of the 'CITGO6,' released from prison in Venezuela - CNN
content: Two Americans, including one member of the 'CITGO6,' released from prison in Venezuela  CNNView Full Coverage on Google News
description: At least one American member of the so-called CITGO 6 has been released from prison in Venezuela, a lawyer assisting several of the CITGO 6 and a spokesman from a Venezuelan nongovernmental organization that's providing legal assistance to prisoners in the country both told CNN.
